raw_data.title: Engagement Manager
raw_data.description: Professional Services -- Manage the entire client engagement process, from scoping the engagement, data capture, data analysis, engagement delivery and software training.  Additionally, the engagement manager is responsible for communications and scheduling between the client and the engagement team. Consulting experience in using data analysis to generate strategic insights for corporate and government stakeholders.

raw_data.title: Senior Data Analyst
raw_data.description: Professional Services --Identify, capture and structure data sets applicable to the engagement requirements.  Expert in Quid’s propriety data capture and processing techniques.  Fluency in at least 1 other language other than English.

raw_data.title: Intelligence Analyst
raw_data.description: Professional Services -- Gather requirements from client, formulate and execute on methodologies for data analysis, interpret results from the Quid software, present findings to client and train client on using the Quid software. Subject matter expert in various technology areas, with experience in quantitate analysis and executive-level synthesis of complex information.

raw_data.title: Senior Engineer
raw_data.description: Professional Services -- Configure Quid software for client requirements and install Quid software onto local client machines.  If adjustments to other software in the Quid technology stack are necessary, the Senior Engineer will perform these tasks. Experienced engineer fluent in numerous computational languages, including Chef, Ruby, Rails, Git, MySQL, Python, Hadoop, Nginx, Syslong, Java, PHP, HTML, CSS and JavaScript and ability to work with client firewalls through knowledge in VPN and firewalls systems.

raw_data.title: Data Scientist
raw_data.description: Professional Services -- Develop and adjust algorithms for data computation and advise the Quid engagement team and client on methodologies for data capture, analysis and visualization. Data analysis algorithm design, complexity reduction and quantitative visualization.  Fluent in numerous computational languages including MySQL, Python and Hadoop.

raw_data.title: Quantitative Analyst
raw_data.description: Professional Services -- Support the client and the Quid engagement team in processing, visualizing and interpreting data from data packs. Quantitative analysis, specifically in using natural language processing techniques to structure and process large text-data sets. Visualizing data and constructing semantic networks.
